{"word":"G459 - ἄνομος - ánomos - an'-om-os - Without law","slug":"G459","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄνομος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ánomos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>an'-om-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Without law"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - anomos</b> - <i>an'-om-os</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G3551\">G3551</a>; <i>lawless</i>, that is, (negatively) <i>not subject to</i> (the Jewish) <i>law</i>; (by implication a <i>Gentile</i>), or (positively) <i>wicked:</i> - without law, lawless, transgressor, unlawful, wicked."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1772\">G1772</a>, <a href=\"#/G3544\">G3544</a>, <a href=\"#/G3545\">G3545</a>, <a href=\"#/G3547\">G3547</a>, <a href=\"#/G3548\">G3548</a>, <a href=\"#/G3549\">G3549</a>, <a href=\"#/G3550\">G3550</a>, <a href=\"#/G3551\">G3551</a>, <a href=\"#/G3891\">G3891</a>, <a href=\"#/G3892\">G3892</a>, <a href=\"#/G458\">G458</a>, <a href=\"#/G460\">G460</a>"}]}